%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20is%20flexing%20his%20wealth%20and%20political%20power%20unlike%20any%20of%20the%20richest%20men%20before%20him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20holds%20the%20microphone%20during%20a%20town%20hall%20in%20Pennsylvania%20where%20he%20discussed%20his%20support%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2F%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67124b1401ea6d83dee21bb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%2C%20stands%20out%20from%20the%20other%20Americans%20who%20preceded%20him%20in%20holding%20the%20same%20title.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Rourke%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20breaking%20ground%20as%20a%20pro-Trump%20megadonor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20he%20may%20not%20donate%20the%20most%20money%20this%20cycle%2C%20Musk%20is%20behaving%20unlike%20any%20of%20the%20uber%20wealthy%20Americans%20before%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Tesla%20CEO%20is%20even%20holding%20his%20own%20series%20of%20political%20rallies%20in%20a%20key%20swing%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica%20has%20never%20seen%20a%20megadonor%20quite%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-campaign-trail-pennsylvania-donald-trump-key-swing-state-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%20held%20a%20town%20hall%20event%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20the%20largest%20swing%20state%20in%20the%202024%20race.%20The%20Tesla%20CEO%20has%20pledged%20to%20hold%20more%20events%20to%20promote%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20election.%20Musk%20has%20also%20seeded%20at%20least%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-america-super-pac-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%2475%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20pro-Trump%20super%20PAC.%20His%20pro-Trump%20group%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-america-pac-targets-young-men-vote-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerica%20PAC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20offers%20to%20pay%20people%20%2447%20if%20they%20get%20supporters%20to%20sign%20a%20petition%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20gives%20the%20outside%20group%20valuable%20data%20on%20potential%20swing%20voters.%20On%20Friday%2C%20Musk%20upped%20the%20offer%20even%20further%2C%20pledging%20%24100%20for%20every%20Pennsylvania%20voter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20is%20sort%20of%20a%20natural%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20%26quot%3B%20journalist%20Roger%20Lowenstein%2C%20who%20wrote%20a%20biography%20about%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20despite%20his%20%24247%20billion%20estimated%20net%20worth%2C%20isn't%20the%20biggest%20donor%20this%20presidential%20election%20cycle.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensecrets.org%2Foutside-spending%2Ftop_donors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenSecrets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20disclosed%20donors%2C%20that%20title%20belongs%20to%20banking%20heir%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-timothy-mellon-robert-kennedy-donald-trump-billionaire-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimothy%20Mellon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20a%20staggering%20%24165%20million%20on%20boosting%20Trump%20and%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20(We%20won't%20know%20the%20full%20extent%20of%202024%20donations%20until%20after%20the%20election%2C%20and%20that%20excludes%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bdark%20money%26quot%3B%20groups%2C%20which%2C%20unlike%20super%20PACs%2C%20do%20not%20have%20to%20disclose%20their%20donors.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20where%20Musk%20stands%20out%20is%20among%20the%20richest%20of%20the%20rich.%20While%20there%20have%20been%20plenty%20of%20wealthy%20mega-donors%20--%20the%20Koch%20brothers%2C%20the%20Adelsons%2C%20Michael%20Bloomberg%2C%20and%20others%20have%20spent%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20on%20super%20PACs%20--%20the%20men%20who%20recently%20preceded%20Musk%20as%20the%20wealthiest%20American%20and%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%20have%20not%20been%20nearly%20as%20involved.%20Musk%20is%20taking%20a%20far%20different%20tact%20than%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20and%20Warren%20Buffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20richest%20man%20in%20the%20world%20fluctuates%20over%20time%20but%20not%20all%20of%20them%20have%20been%20able%20or%20even%20wanted%20to%20spend%20money%20in%20politics%20in%20the%20past%20four%20presidential%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Ciara%20Torres-Spelliscy%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20Stetson%20University%2C%20who%20has%20studied%20big%20money%20in%20politics%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELowenstein%20pointed%20out%20how%20even%20Musk's%20temperament%20differs%20exceptionally%20from%20someone%20like%20Buffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWarren%20just%20couldn't%20be%20more%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Lowenstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20affected%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20Warren%20was%20measured%20to%20be%20the%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20is%20very%20careful%20about%20what%20he%20says.%20He%20does%20not%20like%20personal%20confrontations.%20He%20has%20always%20been%20fascinated%20by%20the%20pragmatic%20issues%20of%20policy.%20He%20doesn't%20get%20out%20there%20and%20say%2C%20you%20know%2C%20so%20and%20so%20is%20running%20the%20country%20or%20all%20the%20name-calling%20that%20is%20the%20political%20system%20these%20days.%20It's%20just%20not%20his%20bag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20Musk%20has%20changed.%20Before%20this%20cycle%2C%20the%20largest%20single%20political%20donation%20he%20had%20ever%20given%20was%20%2475%2C000%20to%20Californians%20for%20Clean%20Alternative%20Energy%20in%202006.%20His%20final%202024%20total%20is%20already%20more%20than%201%2C000%20times%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223949%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20with%20former%20president%20Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6707dba9a70318649280d155%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222633%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMusk%20spoke%20at%20Trump's%20rally%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20where%20the%20former%20president%20returned%20for%20a%20major%20event%20at%20the%20site%20of%20his%20first%20assassination%20attempt.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Anna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20what%20the%20South%20African-born%20tech%20titan%20has%20in%20store%2C%20but%20already%20he%20is%20showing%20an%20openness%20to%20rely%20on%20his%20fortune%20and%20his%20businesses%20in%20distinct%20ways%20the%20other%20three%20have%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20look%20at%20how%20Musk%20has%20shaped%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%20It%20begins%20with%20his%20own%20account%2C%20which%20has%20roughly%20202%20million%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20once%20said%20he%20voted%20for%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20has%20pushed%20memes%20and%20misinformation%20on%20the%20platform%20as%20he's%20become%20increasingly%20vocal%20about%20his%20views.%20He%20also%20lifted%20bans%20on%20Trump%20and%20other%20right-wing%20voices.%20According%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20X%20blocked%20links%20to%20a%20report%20with%20hacked%20information%20about%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%2C%20Trump's%20running%20mate%2C%20after%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20reached%20out.%20Recently%2C%20Musk's%20company%20seized%20the%20%40America%20handle%20to%20boost%20his%20super%20PAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post-%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitizens-united-supreme-court-precedent-political-hypocricy-desantis-disney-feud-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizens%20United%3C%2Fa%3E%20world%2C%20the%20nation's%20billionaires%20have%20dug%20deep%20to%20support%20outside%20organizations%20whose%20ad%20spending%20blitzes%20can%20shape%20elections.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20hard%20ban%20on%20campaigns%20coordinating%20with%20super%20PACs%2C%20a%20limit%20that%20always%20allowed%20for%20some%20creative%20loopholes%2C%20has%20been%20further%20eroded.%20Super%20PACs%20can%20now%20explicitly%20partner%20with%20the%20campaigns%20on%20get-out-the-vote%20efforts%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Trump's%20campaign%20is%20relying%20on%20America%20PAC%20along%20with%20other%20outside%20groups%20to%20make%20up%20the%20difference%20for%20this%20once%20critical%20role%20for%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22254490b1-6509-4044-ae33-54464a618e95%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECitizens%20United%20blew%20open%20the%20door%20to%20big%20money%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%202010%20landmark%20decision%20and%20related%20lower%20court%20rulings%20opened%20the%20door%20to%20super%20PACs.%20There%20was%20almost%20immediate%20concern%20about%20how%20the%20nation's%20wealthiest%20would%20shape%20elections%2C%20especially%20presidential%20races.%20According%20to%20reporter%20Ken%20Vogel's%202012%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BBig%20Money%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20told%20a%20room%20that%20included%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20then-the%20wealthiest%20American%20and%20previously%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%2C%20that%20he%20and%20a%20small%20group%20of%20people%20now%20had%20outsize%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20now%20have%20the%20potential%20of%20200%20people%20deciding%20who%20ends%20up%20being%20elected%20president%20every%20single%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Obama%20told%20the%20room%20that%20also%20included%20Steve%20Ballmer%2C%20who%20later%20replaced%20Gates%20as%20Microsoft%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Buffett%2C%20who%20briefly%20replaced%20Gates%20as%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%20in%202008%2C%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20super%20PAC%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20democracy%20go%20in%20that%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20told%20Berkshire%20Hathway%20shareholders%20during%20an%20open%20Q%20and%20A%20at%20the%20multinational's%202012%20meeting%20in%20Omaha.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20some%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20that%20Buffett%20and%20Gates%20didn't%20have%20political%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oracle%20of%20Omaha%20was%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Obama%20administration's%20push%20to%20raise%20taxes%20on%20the%20wealthy%2C%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BBuffett%20rule.%26quot%3B%20And%20during%20a%202008%20presidential%20debate%2C%20both%20Obama%20and%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee%20John%20McCain%20floated%20the%20investor%20as%20a%20potential%20Treasury%20secretary.%20(Buffett%20never%20joined%20the%20Obama%20administration.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20also%20publicly%20endorsed%20Hillary%20Clinton%20in%202016%20and%20Joe%20Biden%20in%202020.%20He%20held%20a%20fundraiser%20for%20Obama%20in%202012.%20Thanks%20to%20Nebraska's%20way%20of%20awarding%20Electoral%20College%20votes%2C%20he's%20also%20lived%20through%20the%20era%20in%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nebraska-2nd-electoral-college-vote-omaha-harris-mcdonnell-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENebraska%202nd%20Congressional%20Distric%3C%2Fa%3Et%2C%20which%20covers%20Omaha%20and%20some%20of%20the%20metro%20area%2C%20has%20become%20a%20fierce%20political%20battleground.%20The%20city's%20oracle%20has%20yet%20to%20make%20a%202024%20endorsement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Warren%20Buffett%20speaks%20at%20a%202016%20rally%20in%20Omaha%20where%20he%20talked%20about%20his%20support%20for%20Hillary%20Clinton%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671268b7a0a0cc14f221f8dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221472%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuffett%20spoke%20at%20a%202016%20rally%20in%20Omaha%2C%20showcasing%20his%20support%20for%20Hillary%20Clinton.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Pope%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20praised%20Harris%20after%20she%20replaced%20Biden%20earlier%20this%20summer.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20a%20more%20outspoken%20critic%20of%20Trump.%20Gates%2C%20through%20his%20and%20his%20now-ex-wife%20Melinda%20French%20Gates'%20foundation%2C%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20US%20response%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20He%20also%20arguably%20held%20the%20largest%20media%20presence%20of%20the%20American%20billionaires%20until%20Musk%20rocketed%20into%20the%20top%20slot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20other%20recent%20wealthiest%20men%20have%20come%20close%20to%20Musk's%20super%20PAC%20spending.%20Bezos%20made%20the%20biggest%20splash%20in%202018%20when%20they%20donated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2Fjeff-bezos-donates-10-million-to-super-pacwith-honor-fund.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2410%20million%20to%20With%20Honor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20super%20PAC%20that%20supported%20veteran%20candidates.%20Unlike%20America%20PAC%2C%20though%2C%20With%20Honor%20was%20geared%20to%20support%20candidates%20from%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Buffett%20and%20Bezos%20also%20held%20or%20held%20stakes%20in%20media%20companies.%20Bezos%20still%20owns%20The%20Washington%20Post%20(which%2C%20full%20disclosure%2C%20previously%20employed%20me.)%20But%20neither%20man%20positioned%20those%20publications%20in%20the%20way%20Musk%20has%20harnessed%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20unofficial%20group%2C%20Buffett%20was%20arguably%20the%20best%20positioned%20for%20a%20career%20in%20politics.%20While%20he's%20most%20associated%20with%20Nebraska's%20largest%20city%2C%20he%20was%20born%20in%20the%20nation's%20capital%2C%20the%20son%20of%20an%20avowed%20anti-Communist%20congressman.%20Instead%2C%20he%20has%20pursued%20a%20much%20softer%20and%20less%20public%20power%20flexing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20pretty%20good%20listening%20post%2C%20and%20for%20those%20who%20want%2C%20a%20pretty%20good%20advice%20giver%2C%26quot%3B%20Lowenstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20he%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20influence.%20Obviously%2C%20that%20effectiveness%20wouldn't%20be%20there%20if%20it%20became%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-superpac-donations-politics-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729420982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67124b32a0a0cc14f221f057%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-superpac-donations-politics-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20is%20behaving%20unlike%20any%20of%20the%20uber-wealthy%20Americans%20before%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-superpac-donations-politics-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Latest%20LIVE%3A%20BJP%20releases%20first%20list%20for%20Maharashtra%20polls%3B%20fields%20Fadnavis%20from%20Nagpur%20South%20West%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729420641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-pm-modi-to-lay-foundation-stone-for-various-developmental-projects-in-varanasi-today-124102000068_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Catch%20all%20the%20latest%20news%20updates%20from%20around%20the%20world%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22D%20Fadnavis%20Among%20Heavyweights%20In%20BJP's%201st%20Maharashtra%20Candidates%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20is%20among%20the%20heavyweight%20names%20in%20the%20BJP's%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20November%2020%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls.%20The%20list%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20this%20afternoon%2C%20has%2099%20names.%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20has%20288%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20contesting%20151%20of%20them.%20The%20remaining%20seats%20are%20being%20contested%20by%20the%20BJP's%20allies%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20is%20contesting%20from%20Nagpur%20West%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20has%20represented%20since%202009.%20Nagpur%20is%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20represents%20the%20parliamentary%20seat%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Of%20the%20six%20Assembly%20segments%20part%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20four%20are%20held%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20heavyweights%2C%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%20is%20contesting%20from%20Kamthi%2C%20also%20in%20Nagpur%20district.%20Incumbent%20state%20minister%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Ballarpur%20seat%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Raosaheb%20Danve's%20son%20Santosh%20is%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20Bhokardan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20Sreejaya%20Chavan%20in%20Bhokar%3B%20she%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20who%20switched%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20BJP%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20is%20now%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Kotecha%2C%20sitting%20MLA%20from%20Mulund%2C%20has%20been%20repeated%20as%20the%20candidate%20and%20three-time%20legislator%20Ram%20Kadam%20will%20contest%20from%20Mumbai's%20Ghatkopar%20West%20seat%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Mumbai%20chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%20will%20contest%20from%20Vandre%20West%20and%20state%20minister%20Chandrakant%20Patil%20from%20Kothrud.%20Mr%20Shelar's%20brother%20has%20also%20got%20a%20poll%20pass%20and%20will%20contest%20in%20Malad%20West.%C2%A0Subhash%20Deshmukh%20is%20BJP's%20candidate%20in%20Solapur%20and%20Nitesh%20Rane%2C%20son%20of%20veteran%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Narayan%20Rane%2C%20is%20contesting%20in%20Kankavli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20first%20list%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20election%20has%2013%20women%20candidates%2C%20six%20candidates%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20four%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20repeated%20many%20sitting%20MLAs%20as%20candidates%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20party%20is%20known%20to%20replace%20most%20sitting%20representatives%20in%20state%20and%20national%20polls%20to%20neutralise%20the%20effects%20of%20anti-incumbency%20and%20provide%20voters%20with%20a%20fresh%20option.%20Its%20decision%20to%20stick%20with%20sitting%20MLAs%20in%20this%20election%20suggests%20that%20it%20is%20confident%20ahead%20of%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20poll%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20BJP-Sena-NCP%20alliance%20had%20suffered%20a%20setback%2C%20winning%20just%2017%20out%20of%20the%2048%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20bloc%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20Congress%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stellar%20show%2C%20winning%2030%20seats%20in%20the%20politically%20significant%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729420620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fdinkafk_devendra-fadnavis-gen