3Edeflation%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20possibility%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20demand%20would%20cause%20wages%20and%20prices%20to%20spiral%20downward%2C%20a%20trap%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-economy-deflation-unemployment-job-market-recession-outlook-paul-krugman-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextremely%20difficult%20to%20escape%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20an%20effort%20to%20avoid%20that%20fate%2C%20policymakers%20in%20Washington%20pushed%20interest%20rates%20down%20to%20zero%20and%20encouraged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftbank-crashing-investments-uber-wework-monopoly-failure-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20kinds%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlatans-show-up-when-wall-street-stock-market-gets-weird-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisky%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwilight-of-tech-gods-recession-stock-market-crash-silicon-valley-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebehavior%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackmans-big-pharma-trade-is-making-wall-street-a-super-awkward-place-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamong%3C%2Fa%3E%20investors%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20everyday%20consumers.%20Investors%20trying%20to%20reach%20their%20benchmarks%20%26quot%3Bhad%20to%20creep%20out%20on%20the%20risk%20spectrum%2C%26quot%3B%20Josh%20Hirt%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Vanguard%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BSupercheap%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20businesses%20to%20%26quot%3Boverexpand%20and%20overhire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pro-risk%20environment%20had%20some%20earth-shifting%20consequences.%20Silicon%20Valley%20put%20the%20internet%20on%20our%20phones%2C%20China%20blew%20a%20massive%20bubble%20in%20its%20property%20market%2C%20and%20the%20world%20started%20investing%20in%20renewable%20energy.%20But%20low%20interest%20rates%20did%20little%20to%20boost%20demand%2C%20and%20the%20economy%20consistently%20grew%20slower%20than%20it%20did%20before%20the%20crash%2C%20never%20notching%20above%203%25%20GDP%20growth.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20massive%20government%20stimulus%2C%20spurred%20by%20the%20pandemic%2C%20that%20the%20economy%20reached%20escape%20velocity%2C%20pushing%20up%20wages%20and%20starting%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20healthy%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20economists%20say%2C%20we're%20entering%20a%20supercycle%20that%20will%20be%20characterized%20by%20three%20sweeping%20forces.%20First%2C%20higher%20interest%20rates%20will%20reward%20savers%2C%20making%20it%20more%20expensive%20to%20take%20risks.%20Second%2C%20geopolitical%20and%20economic%20volatility%20will%20generate%20inflationary%20effects%2C%20reintroducing%20the%20specter%20of%20soaring%20prices.%20And%20third%2C%20industrial%20planning%20will%20be%20increasingly%20influenced%20by%20national-security%20concerns%2C%20altering%20supply%20chains%20across%20industries.%20How%20low%20interest%20rates%20wind%20up%20settling%20will%20establish%20a%20new%20gravitational%20pull%20in%20global%20markets%2C%20recalibrating%20the%20forces%20that%20determine%20where%20the%20economy%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20grow%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20investment%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20supercycle%20%26quot%3Bputs%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20completely%20new%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Silas%20Myers%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Mar%20Vista%20Investments%2C%20which%20oversees%20%244%20billion%20in%20assets.%20He%20warns%20that%20an%20entire%20generation%20of%20investors%2C%20lenders%2C%20and%20entrepreneurs%20have%20failed%20to%20embrace%20the%20%26quot%3Bprofound%20impact%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20new%20economic%20era%20will%20have%20on%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20in%20a%20time%20that%20was%20less%20demanding%20and%20more%20forgiving%2C%26quot%3B%20Myers%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20time%20is%20ending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20clearest%20signs%20that%20a%20new%20economic%20supercycle%20has%20arrived%20is%20when%20the%20financial%20rules%20go%20topsy-turvy.%20The%20previous%20supercycle%20was%20ushered%20in%20when%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20destruction%20caused%20by%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20cut%20its%20benchmark%20interest%20rate%20to%200%25%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20time%20the%20central%20bank%20went%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20bottom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20structural%20shift%20sent%20shockwaves%20throughout%20the%20world.%20Yields%20on%20Treasury%20bonds%20tanked%2C%20meaning%20investors%20had%20to%20start%20taking%20some%20serious%20risks%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20make%20money.%20This%20new%20adventurism%20pushed%20stocks%20higher%20and%20higher.%20Capital%20went%20flying%20into%20China%20and%20other%20emerging%20markets%20in%20record%20amounts%20%E2%80%94%20some%20%241%20trillion%20in%202010%20alone.%20Venture%20capitalists%20sank%20billions%20into%20companies%20like%20Juicero%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwework-adam-neumann-apartment-startup-investment-silicon-valley-vc-apocalypse-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWeWork%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20had%20no%20viable%20plan%20to%20turn%20a%20profit.%20And%20with%20interest%20rates%20so%20low%2C%20companies%20could%20suddenly%20load%20up%20on%20debt%3A%20From%202007%20to%202017%2C%20global%20nonfinancial%20corporate%20debt%20doubled%2C%20to%20%2466%20trillion.%20Until%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20inflation%20and%20wage%20growth%20both%20remained%20below%203.9%25.%20The%20world%20had%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20new%20supercycle%2C%20money%20managers%20are%20once%20again%20being%20forced%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20changing%20set%20of%20economic%20realities.%20Normally%2C%20when%20the%20Fed%20hikes%20interest%20rates%20rapidly%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20tanks.%20But%20that's%20no%20longer%20true.%20From%202022%20to%202024%2C%20as%20the%20benchmark%20federal%20funds%20rate%20shot%20up%20to%205.5%25%20from%200.5%25%2C%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20soared%20by%2023%25%20and%2022%25.%20Higher%20interest%20rates%20also%20failed%20to%20spur%20widespread%20layoffs%20or%20crater%20the%20economy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-report-labor-market-hiring-layoffs-quits-recession-sahm-rule-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnemployment%20has%20stayed%20below%204.3%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20GDP%20growth%20has%20remained%20solid%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgdp-gross-domestic-product-second-quarter-2024-us-economy-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefying%20fears%20of%20a%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20short%2C%20something%20has%20scrambled%20the%20natural%20interactions%20of%20the%20marketplace.%20It's%20as%20if%20you%20put%20your%20hand%20over%20a%20hot%20stove%20and%20your%20fingers%20turned%20ice%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20explanation%20for%20the%20economy's%20topsy-turvy%20behavior%20is%20a%20change%20in%20what%20economists%20call%20the%20neutral%20interest%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20the%20optimal%20point%20for%20encouraging%20growth%20without%20triggering%20inflation.%20After%20the%20financial%20crisis%20in%202008%2C%20the%20economy%20was%20so%20weak%20that%20the%20neutral%20rate%20went%20to%20zero%20to%20encourage%20money%20to%20flow%20more%20freely.%20But%20now%20the%20market's%20weird%20nature%20may%20be%20signaling%20that%20the%20neutral%20rate%20has%20risen%20above%20the%20Fed's%20ideal%20target%20of%202%25.%20That%20would%20explain%20why%20the%20Fed's%20higher%20rates%20are%20no%20longer%20putting%20the%20brakes%20on%20growth.%20Fueled%20by%20the%20post-pandemic%20government%20stimulus%2C%20the%20economy's%20baseline%20has%20shifted.%20Over%20at%20Vanguard%2C%20Hirt%20and%20his%20colleagues%20predict%20that%20the%20neutral%20rate%20will%20stay%20higher%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20eventually%20settling%20at%20about%203.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20do%20dip%20below%203.5%25%2C%20the%20Fed%20will%20be%20anchored%20at%20that%20higher%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Hirt%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20economy%20were%20to%20experience%20weakness%20and%20we%20have%20to%20cut%20rates%2C%20we%20still%20don't%20think%20that%20means%20taking%20rates%20back%20to%20zero.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20you're%20a%20boomer%2C%20you've%20probably%20never%20experienced%20a%20world%20with%20this%20high%20a%20neutral%20rate.%20It%20changes%20the%20nature%20of%20risk%2C%20which%20changes%20what%20people%20decide%20to%20do%20with%20money%20on%20micro%20and%20macro%20levels.%20If%20you%20can%20get%20a%20decent%20return%20parking%20your%20money%20in%20ultrasafe%20government%20debt%2C%20why%20risk%20investing%20it%20in%20a%20startup%20or%20stomach%20the%20stock%20market's%20volatility%3F%20This%20isn't%20to%20say%20no%20one%20will%20be%20out%20here%20taking%20risks%20with%20their%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20it%20will%20just%20flow%20in%20different%20directions.%20That's%20because%20consumers%20are%20in%20a%20better%20place%20now%20than%20they%20were%20in%20the%20era%20that%20emerged%20after%20the%20Great%20Recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20extraordinarily%20diverse%20and%20dynamic%20animal%2C%26quot%3B%20Joe%20Quinlan%2C%20the%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20assured%20clients%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%20It's%20%26quot%3Ba%20%2428%20trillion%20hydra-headed%20behemoth%20that%20beats%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20many%20different%20sectors.%26quot%3B%20As%20the%20Fed's%20higher%20rates%20were%20putting%20a%20strain%20on%20rate-sensitive%20sectors%20like%20housing%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20up%2016%25%20of%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20Big%20Tech%20and%20travel-starved%20households%20were%20spending%20money%20fast%20and%20loose.%20The%20experience%20showed%20that%20overall%20consumption%20can%20continue%20to%20rise%20even%20when%20significant%20swaths%20of%20the%20economy%20are%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20can%20we%20expect%20from%20the%20new%20economic%20supercycle%3F%20Like%20every%20cycle%2C%20it%20will%20have%20its%20upsides%20and%20downsides.%20Rising%20interest%20rates%20will%20make%20loans%20more%20expensive%2C%20forcing%20businesses%20to%20make%20more-thoughtful%20decisions%20about%20debt.%20But%20they'll%20also%20boost%20savings%20accounts%20and%20interest%20income.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20faster-growing%20economy%20will%20tighten%20the%20labor%20market%2C%20empowering%20workers%20to%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20a%20larger%20slice%20of%20the%20pie.%20Since%202019%2C%20the%20bottom%2010%25%20of%20earners%20have%20seen%20a%20wage%20increase%20of%2013%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShifting%20away%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bgrow%20at%20all%20costs%26quot%3B%20mindset%20of%20the%20previous%20supercycle%20has%20also%20incentivized%20governments%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20the%20developed%20world%20%E2%80%94%20to%20do%20more%20to%20police%20markets%20and%20protect%20consumers.%20Whether%20it's%20capping%20the%20price%20of%20drugs%20or%20enforcing%20antitrust%20rules%20more%20aggressively%2C%20polls%20suggest%20Americans%20want%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprospect.org%2Feconomy%2F2024-08-27-polling-voters-action-corporate-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20limits%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.yougov.com%2Feconomy%2Farticles%2F47798-most-americans-oppose-monopolies-and-support-antitrust-laws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2021%2F07%2F20%2F56-of-americans-support-more-regulation-of-major-technology-companies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20regulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20safeguard%20citizens.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years%2C%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20has%20begun%20going%20after%20pharmaceutical%20middlemen%2C%20opposing%20mergers%20between%20grocery%20giants%2C%20and%20taking%20big%20swings%20at%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20supercycle%20will%20also%20have%20profound%20consequences%20worldwide%2C%20upending%20how%20and%20where%20money%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20flow.%20In%20China%2C%20the%20debt%20bubble%20that%20formed%20in%20the%20property%20sector%20during%20the%20previous%20cycle%20is%20sucking%20cash%20away%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-stimulus-plan-wall-street-stock-market-economy-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusinesses%20and%20households%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20undermining%20China's%20bid%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20leading%20economic%20superpower.%20And%20with%20Europe%20growing%20more%20slowly%20than%20the%20US%2C%20foreign%20investors%20are%20steering%20more%20of%20their%20money%20to%20America.%20In%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20foreign%20investors%20owned%20%248.2%20trillion%20worth%20of%20US%20Treasury%20bonds%2C%20up%20by%207.3%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%20Foreign%20investment%20is%20also%20soaring%20in%20US%20corporate%20bonds%20(up%20by%209.8%25)%20and%20US%20equities%20(up%20by%2023%25).%20Quinlan%20says%20he%20expects%20the%20US%20economy%20to%20continue%20outperforming%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20given%20the%20fiscal%20and%20demographic%20challenges%20facing%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20China.%20In%20an%20era%20of%20increasing%20instability%2C%20when%20former%20sources%20of%20growth%20are%20flailing%2C%20the%20United%20States%20is%20widely%20viewed%20as%20the%20safest%20place%20to%20find%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20lost%20on%20investors%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20US%20economy%20remains%20among%20the%20most%20competitive%2C%20innovative%2C%20and%20resilient%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Quinlan%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20to%20investors.%20%26quot%3BAerospace%20or%20agriculture%2C%20energy%20or%20entertainment%2C%20transportation%20or%20technology%2C%20goods%20or%20services%20%E2%80%94%20pick%20any%20sector%20or%20activity%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20the%20US%20leads%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20All%20of%20this%20has%20helped%20fuel%20demand%20among%20foreign%20investors%20for%20US%20securities%20of%20all%20stripes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20economic%20diversification%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20give%20it%20a%20leg%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20volatile%20features%20of%20the%20new%20era%3A%20trade%20conflict.%20The%20US%20and%20China%20are%20already%20battling%20for%20control%20over%20critical%20industries%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jiinping-future-tech-global-economy-semiconductors-military-failing-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemiconductors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-crushing-us-america-battle-energy-evs-batteries-tech-war-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatteries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-crush-tesla-elon-musk-american-ev-industry-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20tit%20for%20tat%20will%20be%20especially%20costly%20for%20less%20diversified%20economies.%20Germany's%20dependence%20on%20manufacturing%2C%20for%20example%2C%20places%20its%20most%20essential%20industries%20on%20a%20collision%20course%20with%20China's%20ambitions.%20And%20while%20the%20United%20States%20is%20well%20positioned%20to%20weather%20the%20storm%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20won't%20be%20rough.%20The%20world%20has%20never%20faced%20a%20challenge%20like%20the%20skyrocketing%20flow%20of%20exports%20from%20China%20up%20and%20down%20the%20value%20chain.%20It's%20a%20dynamic%20that%20threatens%20to%20imbalance%20international%20trade%20by%20flooding%20the%20market%20with%20cheap%20goods%20of%20all%20kinds.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-shock-explainer-us-economy-trade-dumping-supply-glut-yellen-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20Shock%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20go%20down%20easily%2C%26quot%3B%20Quinlan%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20decade%20we%20have%20become%20accustomed%20to%20the%20economy%20working%20a%20certain%20way%20%E2%80%94%20if%20this%2C%20then%20that.%20As%20a%20new%20supercycle%20emerges%2C%20investors%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20governments%20that%20structured%20themselves%20around%20the%20old%20model%20may%20experience%20acute%20shocks.%20To%20succeed%20in%20this%20unfamiliar%20new%20world%2C%20they'll%20have%20to%20adjust%20their%20expectations%20and%20find%20ways%20to%20harness%20the%20supercycle's%20opportunities.%20It's%20the%20economic%20equivalent%20of%20natural%20selection%3A%20As%20the%20economy%20evolves%2C%20those%20who%20adapt%20will%20be%20most%20likely%20to%20survive.%20The%20days%20of%20economic%20growth%20are%20back.%20The%20future%20belongs%20to%20those%20who%20can%20grow%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flinette-lopez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ELinette%20Lopez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-new-economic-supercycle-growth-inflation-stock-market-global-chaos-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729417562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671165c701ea6d83dee1f138%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-new-economic-supercycle-growth-inflation-stock-market-global-chaos-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20economy%20is%20entering%20a%20bold%20new%20era%20that%20economists%20say%20will%20feature%20more%20inflation%2C%20more%20growth%2C%20and%20more%20chaos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22llopez%40insider.com%20(Linette%20Lopez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-new-economic-supercycle-growth-inflation-stock-market-global-chaos-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Atishi's%20%26quot%3BUnderworld%26quot%3B%20Jab%20At%20Centre%20Over%20Delhi%20Blast%2C%20BJP's%20%26quot%3BPuppet%26quot%3B%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20multi-agency%20investigation%20into%20the%20mysterious%20blast%20in%20Delhi's%20Rohini%20today%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20targeted%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20The%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20controls%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20this%20has%20been%20a%20key%20point%20of%20conflict%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20Delhi's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%2C%20which%20took%20place%20at%207.47%20am%2C%20blew%20off%20a%20wall%20of%20the%20CRPF%20school%20in%20Delhi's%20Prashant%20Vihar.%20While%20no%20one%20was%20injured%2C%20the%20explosion%20shattered%20car%20windows%20and%20damaged%20hoardings%20of%20shops.%20Multiple%20security%20agencies%2C%20including%20Delhi%20Police%20Special%20Cell%2C%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20CRPF%20and%20NSG%2C%20are%20now%20probing%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Ms%20Atishi%20said%20the%20blast%20had%20exposed%20Delhi's%20%26quot%3Bcrumbling%26quot%3B%20law%20and%20order%20system.%20%26quot%3BThe%20responsibility%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Delhi%20is%20with%20BJP's%20central%20government.%20But%20BJP%20ignores%20this%20and%20uses%20its%20time%20to%20disrupt%20the%20work%20of%20Delhi's%20elected%20governments.%20This%20is%20why%20Delhi's%20situation%20is%20now%20that%20of%20Mumbai%20during%20the%20era%20of%20the%20Underworld.%20Bullets%20are%20being%20fired%20in%20the%20open%2C%20gangsters%20are%20extorting%20money%20and%20criminals%20are%20upbeat.%20The%20BJP%20neither%20has%20the%20intent%20nor%20the%20ability%20(to%20handle%20this)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20by%20mistake%2C%20Delhiites%20give%20them%20(BJP)%20charge%20of%20Delhi%20government%2C%20the%20condition%20of%20hospitals%2C%20power%20and%20water%20supply%20will%20become%20the%20same%20as%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Ms%20Atishi's%20charge%2C%20BJP's%20Shazia%20Ilmi%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20puppet%20CM%20is%20known%20for%20this.%20If%20you%20make%20her%20speak%20on%20any%20topic%2C%20it%20is%20always%20about%20the%20Centre.%20Something%20very%20serious%20has%20happened.%20The%20situation%20is%20totally%20in%20control.%20Instead%20of%20expressing%20anxiety%20about%20the%20situation%20and%20(thinking)%20what%20should%20be%20done%2C%20a%20political%20blame%20game%20has%20begun.%20It%20is%20immature%20and%20irresponsible%20to%20always%20do%20politics%20on%20serious%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20are%20due%20in%20February%20and%20the%20AAP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%2010%20years%20now%2C%20is%20pushing%20hard%20to%20win%20a%20third%20term.%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%2C%20stepped%20down%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20last%20month%20and%20said%20he%20would%20return%20to%20the%20top%20office%20only%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20court%26quot%3B%20elects%20him%20again.%20Following%20his%20resignation%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20Atishi%20took%20over%20the%20top%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20the%20Explosives%20Act%20and%20started%20a%20detailed%20probe%20into%20the%20Rohini%20blast.%20Sniffer%20dogs%20and%20forensic%20teams%20have%20visited%20the%20spot%20to%20search%20for%20clues.%20Preliminary%20probe%20suggests%20a%20crude%20bomb%20could%20be%20behind%20the%20explosion.%20Police%20have%20found%20a%20white%20powder-like%20substance%20at%20the%20spot.%20The%20area%20has%20been%20cordoned%20off%20and%20is%20being%20mapped.%20Police%20are%20scanning%20CCTV%20footage%20in%20the%20area%20to%20identify%20who%20planted%20the%20bomb.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20police%20are%20not%20ruling%20out%20a%20conspiracy%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijender%20Gupta%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20MLA%20from%20Rohini%2C%20visited%20the%20blast%20site%20this%20morning.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20relief%20that%20no%20one%20was%20harmed.%20It%20was%20a%20big%20blast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729417500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fa3fq28p8_atishi_625x300_14_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-blast-atishi-delhi-now-like-mumbai-during-underworld-era-atishi-slams-bjp-over-blast-6831564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20multi-agency%20investigation%20into%20the%20mysterious%20blast%20in%20Delhi's%20Rohini%20today%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20targeted%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20national%20capital%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-blast-atishi-delhi-now-like-mumbai-during-underworld-era-atishi-slams-bjp-ov