href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-states-lawsuit-block-save-student-loan-income-driven-repayment-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eran%20into%20legal%20threats%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20groups%20of%20GOP%20state%20attorneys%20general%20and%20culminated%20in%20two%20separate%20lawsuits%2C%20one%20of%20which%20blocked%20any%20future%20loan%20forgiveness%20through%20the%20plan%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20plan%20in%20its%20entirety%20has%20remained%20blocked%20%E2%80%94%20the%208th%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20prohibited%20the%20Education%20Department%20from%20implementing%20any%20provisions%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20until%20the%20court%20issues%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20leaving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-millennial-worried-cheaper-student-loan-payments-relief-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E8%20million%20enrolled%20borrowers%20in%20limbo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20movement%20could%20soon%20be%20made%3B%20on%20October%2024%2C%20a%20Missouri%20court%20will%20hear%20oral%20arguments%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20after%20which%20the%208th%20Circuit%20will%20issue%20its%20final%20decision.%20It%20will%20consider%20the%20key%20arguments%20the%20GOP%20states%20have%20made%20on%20why%20SAVE%20should%20be%20blocked%2C%20including%20the%20plans'%20harm%20to%20student-loan%20company%20Mohela%20and%20the%20states'%20tax%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMOHELA%20faces%20the%20imminent%20loss%20of%20revenue%20in%20its%20role%20as%20a%20servicer%20of%20loans%20owned%20by%20the%20Federal%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20the%20attorneys%20general%20filed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-student-loan-forgiveness-struck-down-mohela-biden-debt-relief-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20same%20argument%3C%2Fa%3E%20GOP%20attorneys%20general%20used%20to%20block%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20last%20summer%2C%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ultimately%20struck%20down.%20They%20had%20argued%20that%20Mohela%2C%20which%20is%20an%20instrumentality%20of%20Missouri%2C%20would%20lose%20revenue%20on%20forgiven%20loans%20despite%20the%20servicer%20having%20previously%20denied%20involvement%20in%20the%20legal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Nahmias%2C%20the%20legal%20director%20of%20the%20UC%20Berkeley%20Center%20for%20Consumer%20Law%20and%20Economic%20Justice%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20given%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20prior%20ruling%2C%20the%20arguments%20the%20states%20are%20making%20this%20time%20around%20could%20prevail%20with%20the%20Missouri%20judges%20during%20oral%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20appellate%20court%20has%20to%20apply%20the%20law%20from%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Nahmias%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20that%20this%20particular%20argument%20that%20Missouri%20and%20the%20states%20are%20making%2C%20even%20if%20I%20believe%20that%20it's%20not%20substantial%2C%20I%20think%20that%20it%20might%20hold%20some%20water%20with%20this%20panel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fcf0e7a-8bee-4936-b656-e6a8b0957a39%5C%22%3EWhere%20borrowers%20stand%20under%20the%20SAVE%20block%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20surprising%20that%20there's%20confusion%20surrounding%20the%20SAVE%20litigation%20%E2%80%94%20there%20have%20been%20a%20number%20of%20different%20court%20rulings%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20that%20impacted%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan.%20For%20now%2C%20borrowers%20can%20focus%20on%20the%208th%20Circuit%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaced%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20on%20the%20plan%20in%20its%20entirety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20will%20determine%20whether%20the%20plan%20will%20ultimately%20be%20implemented%20or%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20August%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-pause-save-plan-no-lower-student-loan-payments-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclined%20to%20allow%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20move%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20implementing%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20while%20the%20legal%20process%20continued%2C%20instead%20referring%20the%20task%20back%20to%20the%208th%20Circuit.%20In%20its%20one-paragraph%20ruling%2C%20the%20nation's%20highest%20court%20said%20that%20it%20expects%20the%208th%20Circuit%20%26quot%3Bwill%20render%20its%20decision%20with%20appropriate%20dispatch%2C%26quot%3B%20encouraging%20the%20court%20to%20move%20quickly%20with%20its%20final%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20when%20exactly%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20will%20be%20made%2C%20and%20the%208th%20Circuit%20might%20look%20at%20the%20broader%20relief%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20as%20context%20to%20make%20its%20decision.%20However%2C%20Nahmias%20said%20that%20the%20arguments%20the%20GOP%20attorneys%20general%20are%20making%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Mohela%20%E2%80%94%20are%20highly%20speculative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20announced%20in%20April%20that%20over%201%20million%20student-loan%20borrowers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-being-transferred-from-mohela-to-new-servicers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewere%20being%20transferred%20from%20Mohela%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20new%20servicers%20upon%20Mohela%20request%20to%20allow%20borrowers%20to%20receive%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20service%20and%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Nahmias%20said%20there%20has%20not%20been%20any%20evidence%20of%20financial%20harm%