ly%20homes%20as%20of%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20as%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20didn't%20cross%20his%20mind%20until%20he%20decided%20to%20list%20one%20of%20his%20own%20properties%3A%20an%20Airbnb%20in%20a%20small%20North%20Carolina%20golf%20haven%20called%20Pinehurst%20that%20wasn't%20bringing%20in%20as%20much%20revenue%20post-Covid.%20Rather%20than%20hire%20an%20agent%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20get%20his%20license%20and%20have%20a%20go%20at%20selling%20it%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20enjoyed%20the%20process%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20his%20desk%20job%2C%20which%20frequently%20triggered%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Sunday%20scaries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20getting%20really%20over%20the%20corporate%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22avery%20helibron%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62212ff3d72a2500197400a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeilbron%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Avery%20Heilbron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMostly%20thanks%20to%20his%20rental%20income%2C%20he%20felt%20financially%20prepared%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20steady%20paycheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20really%20that%20scary%20at%20all%20to%20leave%2C%20especially%20because%20I%20had%20the%20math%20on%20my%20side%20and%20the%20other%20income%20on%20my%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20reserves%20%E2%80%94%20a%20year's%20worth%20of%20mortgages%20for%20everything%2C%20plus%20a%20year's%20worth%20of%20expenses%20for%20my%20life.%20It's%20probably%20pretty%20conservative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20allowed%20him%20to%20jump%20into%20a%20new%20career%20with%20zero%20expectations%20or%20pressure%20to%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20the%20real-estate%20agent%20stuff%20I%20could%20make%20zero%20sales%20and%20still%20be%20totally%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20up%20to%20this%20point%2C%20I've%20come%20close%20to%20completely%20replacing%20my%20W2%20income%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b3541dc-6177-4b19-861d-49aba9c642c1%5C%22%3EBuilding%20wealth%20via%20real%20estate%20investing%3A%20From%20house%20hacking%20to%2014%20units%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHeilbron%2C%20who%20was%2024%20when%20he%20bought%20his%20first%20home%2C%20had%20to%20get%20creative%20to%20notch%20his%20first%20two%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20he%20used%20to%20afford%20his%20duplex%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bhouse%20hacking%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20involves%20renting%20out%20a%20portion%20of%20your%20home%20to%20offset%20your%20mortgage.%20He's%20adamant%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-into-real-estate-on-budget-house-hacking-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20most%20inexpensive%20way%20to%20buy%20real%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20for%20someone%20looking%20to%20get%20their%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20%E2%80%94%20the%20main%20tradeoff%20being%20personal%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20cost-effective%20for%20two%20main%20reasons.%20One%2C%20since%20you're%20actually%20living%20in%20the%20property%2C%20you%20may%20qualify%20for%20an%20FHA%20loan%2C%20which%20is%20a%20government-backed%20mortgage%20that%20allows%20people%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20with%20down%20payments%20as%20low%20as%203.5%25.%20That%20can%20significantly%20lower%20your%20upfront%20costs%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20pricey%20market%20like%20Heilbron%20did%20when%20he%20started%20his%20investing%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20lower%20your%20housing%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20like%20in%20Heilbron's%20case%2C%20completely%20eliminate%20it%20and%20free%20up%20cash%20to%20buy%20more%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20proximity%20to%20tenants%20is%20what%20allowed%20him%20to%20gradually%20expand%20to%2014%20units%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20primary%20residence%2C%20a%20single-family%20home%20in%20Durham.%20It%20has%20a%20750-square-foot%20detached%20garage%20that%20he's%20converting%20into%20a%20rental%20that%20will%20eventually%20help%20offset%20his%20current%20mortgage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22detached%20garage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671292e901ea6d83dee253b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeilbron%20is%20converting%20the%20detached%20garage%20on%20his%20primary%20residence's%20property%20into%20a%20mid-term%20rental.%3Cp%3EAvery%20Heilbron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeilbron's%20past%20side%20hustles%20have%20included%20personal%20coaching%20and%20creating%20branded%20social%20media%20content%2C%20but%20he%20says%20his%20real%20estate%20investments%20are%20the%20primary%20reason%20he%20was%20able%20to%20pivot%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20manages%20a%20mixture%20of%20short-term%20and%20long-term%20rentals%2C%20which%20come%20with%20their%20pros%20and%20cons.%20In%20his%20experience%2C%20the%20short-term%20rental%20business%20is%20more%20lucrative%20but%20requires%20more%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20two%20completely%20different%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20two%20rental%20strategies.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Airbnb%20is%20definitely%20more%20work%2C%20definitely%20not%20what%20I%20would%20consider%20a%20passive%20activity.%20You're%20actively%20thinking%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20make%20it%20better%20%E2%80%94%20and%20checking%20pricing%20and%20all%20that%20stuff%2C%20whereas%20the%20long-term%20you%20just%20sign%20a%20tenant%20and%20might%20have%20a%20couple%20of%20maintenance%20issues%20or%20requests%20throughout%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short-term%20rental%20space%20has%20also%20evolved%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20some%20hosts%20have%20struggled%20during%20an%20era%20coined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-worried-about-airbnb-bust-short-term-rentals-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'Airbnbust%3C%2Fa%3E.'%20It's%20harder%20to%20make%20money%20in%202024%20than%20it%20was%20in%202021%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20were%20to%20just%20buy%20a%20regular%20house%20and%20wanted%20it%20to%20work%20out%20well%2C%20it%20might%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20difficult%20if%20you%20just%20throw%20furniture%20in%20there%20and%20don't%20give%20it%20your%20all.%20Whereas%20in%202021%2C%20you%20could%20kind%20of%20just%20put%20anything%20up%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20it%20seemed%20to%20do%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20Airbnb%20units%2C%20which%20include%20a%20cabin%20and%20tiny%20home%2C%20do%20well%20because%20they%20stand%20out%20and%20offer%20unique%20amenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Airbnb%20homepage%20features%20different%20types%20of%20stays%3B%20you%20can%20click%20on%20tabs%20like%20%26quot%3Bcabins%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Btiny%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Boff-the-grid.%26quot%3B%20Heilbron's%20strategy%20is%20to%20build%20unique%20properties%20that%20fit%20under%20these%20niche%20categories%20and%20eventually%20rank%20high%20on%20those%20specific%20pages.%20He%20also%20gets%20eyeballs%20on%20his%20listings%20from%20the%20Instagram%20page%20he's%20created%20for%20his%20Airbnb%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC-C6BpEu_kW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26