gler.%20The%20second%20most%20Republican%20vehicle%3F%20The%20Jeep%20Gladiator.%20And%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20reddest%20vehicles%20are%20American-made.%20If%20you%20like%20Trump%2C%20you%20probably%20like%20Chevys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eef577ae-00d6-446b-89e7-1387ed3ffdbb%5C%22%3ETop%2010%20most%20Republican%20vehicles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FdsA2f%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22531%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reverse%20was%20true%20for%20blue%20counties.%20The%20most%20Democratic%20vehicle%20in%20America%20is%20the%20Toyota%20Prius.%20And%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20bluest%20vehicles%20are%20foreign-made.%20If%20you%20like%20Biden%2C%20you%20probably%20get%20your%20oil%20changed%20at%20a%20VW%20dealership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22951e1f99-f84d-49be-9311-17ef080c9719%5C%22%3ETop%2010%20most%20Democratic%20vehicles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FUIxo5%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%20%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22536%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20interesting%20of%20all%20are%20the%20vehicles%20that%20appeal%20to%20%3Cem%3Eboth%20%3C%2Fem%3Esides%20of%20the%20political%20divide.%20Despite%20some%20of%20its%20models%20ranking%20high%20with%20Republicans%2C%20the%20purplest%20carmaker%20in%20America%20%E2%80%94%20the%20one%20that%20spans%20the%20widest%20range%20on%20the%20red-blue%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20is%20Jeep.%20The%20automaker%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20has%20made%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20transcend%20tribalism%20and%20for