%20In%20retaliation%2C%20since%20October%201%20this%20year%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20full-scale%20military%20operations%20in%20Southern%20Lebanon%20and%20Beirut%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20create%20a%20buffer%20zone%20free%20of%20the%20Hezbollah's%20presence%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Sinwar's%20death%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20European%20leaders%20have%20renewed%20calls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Biden%20said%20Sinwar's%20death%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20opportunity%20to%20seek%20a%20path%20to%20peace%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Two%20Aspects%20To%20Sinwar's%20Death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20ceasefire%20has%20proved%20elusive%20since%20Israel's%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%20All%20that%20has%20been%20made%20possible%20is%20a%20few%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20pauses%26quot%3B%20to%20let%20aid%20reach%20the%20besieged%20people%20in%20Gaza.%20Israel%20has%20resisted%20all%20calls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20alleging%20that%20any%20such%20step%20would%20be%20exploited%20by%20the%20Hamas%20to%20regroup%20and%20remobilise.%20Shortly%20after%20Sinwar's%20death%2C%20Danny%20Danon%2C%20Israel's%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BYesterday%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20many%20asked%20why%20we%20are%20still%20in%20Gaza%20a%20year%20after%20the%20October%207th%20atrocities.%20Today%20they%20got%20the%20answer.%20No%20terrorist%20is%20immune%20to%20the%20long%20arm%20of%20the%20IDF.%20We%20will%20not%20stop%20until%20we%20bring%20home%20all%20of%20our%20hostages%20and%20eliminate%20the%20Hamas%20monsters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20aspects%20to%20Sinwar's%20death.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20defence%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20pictures%20of%20the%20last%20moments%20leading%20to%20Sinwar's%20death%20show%20him%20sitting%20alone%20in%20a%20room%20above%20ground.%20The%20scene%20points%20to%20significant%20damage%20inflicted%20by%20the%20IDF%20on%20the%20numerous%20underground%20tunnels%20that%20the%20Hamas%20used.%20With%20the%20death%20of%20numerous%20high-profile%20leaders%20of%20both%20the%20Hamas%20and%20the%20Hezbollah%2C%20the%20organisations%20are%20in%20disarray.%20The%20former%2C%20especially%2C%20has%20been%20heavily%20dismantled.%20This%20factor%20alone%20may%20push%20its%20other%20members%20to%20surrender%20and%20release%20the%20100-odd%20Israeli%20hostages%20still%20being%20held%20captive%20in%20the%20Strip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20between%20the%20US%2C%20Israel%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20Arab%20states%20have%20also%20revolved%20around%20a%20plan%20whereby%20post-war%20Gaza%20would%20see%20joint-Arab%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Question%20Of%20Hostages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20turned%20Gaza%20into%20rubble.%20Even%20with%2042%2C000%20dead%20in%20the%20strip%2C%20even%20after%20a%20year%20of%20war%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20one%20of%20its%20major%20objectives%20%E2%80%94the%20release%20of%20all%20hostages.%20While%20about%20120-odd%20hostages%20have%20been%20freed%E2%80%94thanks%20to%20major%20back-channel%20efforts%20by%20Qatar%2C%20Egypt%2C%20and%20the%20US%E2%80%94a%20number%20of%20them%20died%20in%20captivity%2C%20while%20about%20100-odd%20hostages%20are%20still%20with%20the%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20high-profile%20assassinations%20like%20Sinwar's%20are%20not%20something%20new%20for%20the%20Hamas.%20Israel%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20carrying%20out%20such%20operations%2C%20and%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20the%20Hamas%20has%20only%20emerged%20militarily%20stronger%2C%20inflicting%20increasingly%20more%20brutal%20attacks%20on%20Israelis.%20The%20October%207%20attacks%20were%20a%20culmination%20of%20this%20history%2C%C2%A0when%20Hamas%20launched%20multi-pronged%20strikes%20on%20Israel%20from%20land%2C%20sea%2C%20and%20air%2C%20carefully%20dodging%20all%20surveillance%20and%20air%20defence%20systems.%C2%A0%C2%A0launched%20multi-pronged%20strikes%20on%20Israel%20from%20land%2C%20sea%2C%20and%20air%2C%20carefully%20dodging%20all%20surveillance%20and%20air%20defence%20systems.%C2%A0%2C%20carefully%20dodging%20all%20surveillance%20and%20air%20defence%20systems.%20Many%2C%20including%20those%20inside%20Israel%2C%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20unprecedented%20destruction%20wrought%20by%20Israel%20in%20Gaza%20may%20just%20be%20what%20incentivises%20others%20to%20join%20the%20ranks%20of%20Hamas%20and%20continue%20its%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Hamas%20has%20kept%20up%20the%20bravado%20up%20too.%20Sinwar's%20long-time%20deputy%2C%20Khalil%20al-Hayya%2C%20has%20said%20that%20Sinwar's%20death%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20only%20increase%20the%20strength%20and%20resolve%20of%20Hamas%20and%20our%20resistance%E2%80%9D.%20What%20is%20also%20interesting%20is%20that%20Fatah%2C%20the%20Hamas's%20arch-rival%20and%20which%20together%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organisation%20had%20promised%20to%20eschew%20any%20violence%20against%20Israel%2C%20has%20also%20officially%20released%20a%20statement%20mourning%20the%20death%20of%20%26quot%3Bmartyr%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20%26quot%3B.%20Hence%2C%20while%20the%20world%20would%20want%20nothing%20more%20for%20the%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20and%20a%20ceasefire%20reached%2C%20whether%20it%20will%20actually%20happen%20remains%20anyone's%20guess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetanyahu's%20Quandary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETellingly%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20also%20not%20committed%20to%20any%20ceasefire.%20%26quot%3BThe%20war%20...%20is%20not%20over%20yet.%20And%20it%20is%20difficult%2C%20and%20it%20exacts%20heavy%20prices%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20after%20Sinwar's%20death.%20He%20also%20had%20a%20message%20for%20the%20Hamas%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20lays%20down%20his%20weapon%20and%20returns%20our%20hostages%E2%80%94we%20will%20allow%20him%20to%20go%20on%20living.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Netanyahu%20would%20hope%20for%20this%20to%20happen.%20His%20war%20on%20Gaza%20has%20not%20exactly%20provided%20him%20the%20domestic%20support%20he%20had%20hoped%20for%2C%20with%20many%20in%20his%20own%20country%20opposing%20it.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20hostages%20from%20October%207%20remain%20captive%20in%20Gaza%2C%20it%20would%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20failure.%20Besides%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20IDF%20soldiers%20dead%20and%20the%20economy%20taking%20an%20unprecedented%20hit%2C%20the%20war%20has%20taken%20a%20great%20toll%20on%20the%20Israeli%20people%20themselves.%20The%20conflict%20has%20significantly%20escalated%20with%20Israel's%20air%20and%20ground%20operations%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20which%20have%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C000%20people%20and%20displaced%20many%20Lebanese%20civilians.%20After%20the%20death%20of%20Hezbollah%20chief%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20Iran%20launched%20a%20barrage%20of%20missiles%20directly%20at%20Israel%2C%20the%20second%20time%20it%20has%20done%20so%20this%20year.%20Israel%20has%20vowed%20to%20avenge%20this.%20And%20in%20another%20symbolic%20escalation%2C%20none%20other%20than%20Netanyahu's%20house%20was%20targeted%20in%20a%20Hezbollah%20drone%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarris%20Or%20Trump%2C%20US%20Support%20May%20Continue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20little%20incentive%20for%20Netanyahu's%20government%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20ceasefire%20now%2C%20when%20the%20IDF's%20successes%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20the%20deaths%20of%20those%20like%20Nasrallah%20and%20Sinwar%20are%20being%20hailed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20people%20as%20achievements%20after%20a%20year%20of%20opposition%2C%20which%20even%20saw%20calls%20for%20the%20government%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20with%20US%20elections%20just%20weeks%20away%2C%20Netanyahu%20understands%20that%20he%20would%20likely%20get%20a%20free%20pass.%20No%20matter%20what%20US%20Vice%20President%20and%20Democrat%20Presidential%20candidate%20Kamala%20Harris's%20domestic%20compulsions%20may%20be%2C%20overall%2C%20there%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20any%20major%20opposition%20to%20Israel's%20wars.%20And%20in%20case%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20the%20Republicans%20form%20the%20next%20government%2C%20they%20are%20only%20expected%20to%20take%20a%20harsher%20stance%20against%20Iran.%20Marwan%20al-Muasher%2C%20Jordan's%20former%20foreign%20minister%20and%20now%20Vice-President%20for%20Studies%20at%20the%20U.S.-based%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace%2C%20sums%20it%20up%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20reason%20for%20Netanyahu%20to%20stop%20his%20wars%20before%20the%20American%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20it%20seems%20both%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20led%20by%20some%20unknown-to-us%2C%20apocalyptic%20vision%2C%20are%20fighting%20to%20the%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Aditi%20Bhaduri%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst.%20She%20has%20translated%20the%20works%20of%20Nicholas%20Roerich%20from%20Russian%20to%20English)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729413120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fb7mgppk8_israel_625x300_20_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-has-little-reason-to-end-its-war-on-gaza-even-with-yahya-sinwar-dead-6831240%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20US%20elections%20just%20weeks%20away%2C%20Israeli%20PM%20Netanyahu%20understands%20that%20he%20would%20likely%20get%20a%20free%20pass%2C%20whether%20Trump%20becomes%20President%20or%20Kamala%20Harris.%22%2C%22au