3A%22%3Cp%3EAstronomers%20have%20discovered%20a%20remarkably%20orderly%20distant%20galaxy%C2%A0named%20REBELS-25%20using%20the%20Atacama%20Large%20Millimetre%2Fsubmillimetre%20Array%20(ALMA)%20telescope%2C%20which%20shows%20surprising%20similarities%20to%20the%20Milky%20Way%20despite%20being%20much%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EREBELS-25%20exhibits%20a%20rotation-dominated%20structure%2C%20unlike%20expectations%20that%20early%20systems%20would%20appear%20clumpy%20and%20chaotic.%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20our%20understanding%20of%20galaxy%20formation%2C%20we%20expect%20most%20early%20systems%20to%20be%20small%20and%20messy-looking%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jacqueline%20Hodge%2C%20an%20astronomer%20at%20Leiden%20University%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F10%2F16%2Fscience%2Frebels-25-disc-galaxy-paper-scli-intl%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thus%2C%20this%20discovery%C2%A0challenges%20the%20current%20understanding%20of%20cosmic%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDave%20Clements%2C%20an%20astrophysicist%20from%20Imperial%20College%20London%2C%20called%20the%20galaxy's%C2%A0disc-like%20structure%20unexpected%20for%20such%20an%20early%20stage%20in%20the%20universe's%20development.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20universe%20back%20then%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20chaotic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Clements%20explained.%20He%20questioned%20whether%20REBELS-25%20is%20an%20outlier%20or%20indicative%20of%20flawed%20galaxy%20formation%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20galaxy%20is%20seen%20as%20it%20was%20when%20the%20Universe%20was%20only%20700%20million%20years%20old.%20This%20relatively%20short%20timeline%20for%20REBELS-25's%20formation%20contradicts%20the%20traditional%20view%20of%20galaxies%20evolving%20slowly%20over%20billions%20of%20years.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CSeeing%20a%20galaxy%20with%20such%20similarities%20to%20our%20own%20Milky%20Way...%20challenges%20our%20understanding%20of%20how%20quickly%20galaxies%20in%20the%20early%20Universe%20evolve%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20Lucie%20Rowland%2C%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%20and%20a%20doctoral%20student%20at%20Leiden%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Blain%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20astrophysics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Leicester%2C%20described%20the%20discovery%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20bit%20unusual%2C%E2%80%9D%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20not%20revolutionary%20but%20noteworthy.%20He%20explained%20how%20ALMA%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20finding%20these%20galaxies%2C%20which%20would%20otherwise%20be%20too%20faint%20to%20detect.%20Mr%20Blain%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CALMA%20also%20reveals%20details%20finer%20than%20earlier%20telescopes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20has%20been%20accepted%20for%20publication%20in%20the%20Monthly%20Notices%20of%20the%20Royal%20Astronomical%20Society%2C%20and%20further%20observations%20are%20planned%20to%20confirm%20the%20presence%20of%20spiral%20arms%20and%20other%20advanced%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729407540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fptk06img_rebels25-galaxy_625x300_20_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnewly-found-galaxy-resembles-milky-way-challenging-views-on-cosmic-development-6830068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20research%2C%20led%20by%20scientists%20from%20Leiden%20University%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20reveals%20that%20REBELS-25%20is%20much%20more%20orderly%20than%20what%20current%20scientific%20models%20suggest%20for%20galaxies%20of%20its%20age.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnewly-found-galaxy-resembles-milky-way-challenging-views-on-cosmic-development-6830068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kajol%20celebrates%2029%20years%20of%20'DDLJ%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729407367000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2F