20is%20still%20better).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20India%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20vindicated%20Jasprit%C2%A0Bumrah's%20promotion%20as%20the%20vice-captain%20for%20the%20three-Test%20series%20against%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20elevation%20to%20vice-captaincy%20for%20the%20Test%20series%2C%20beginning%20here%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20came%20as%20a%20bit%20of%20surprise%20as%20India%20did%20not%20have%20a%20deputy%20to%20Rohit%20in%20the%20recent%20series%20against%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20has%20been%20viewed%20as%20a%20precursor%20to%C2%A0Bumrah%C2%A0stepping%20in%20as%20India's%20skipper%20during%20the%20tour%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%C2%A0Bumrah%C2%A0has%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket.%20I've%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20with%20him.%20He%20understands%20the%20game%20pretty%20well.%20He's%20got%20a%20good%20head%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20When%20you%20talk%20to%20him%2C%20he%20understands%20the%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTactically%2C%20I%20can't%20say%20much%20because%20he%20has%20not%20captained%20much.%20He%20was%20captain%20in%20one%20Test%20match%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20T20s%2C%20I%20guess%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729402860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F86vcr5go_jasprit-bumrah_625x300_18_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnaseem-shah-is-better-than-jasprit-bumrah-pakistan-fast-bowler-makes-shocking-claim-6830196%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20fast%20bowler%20Ihsanullah%20grabbed%20the%20headlines%20following%20a%20sensational%20comment%20on%20India%20star%20pacer%20Jaspr