0taste%2C%20and%20some%20of%20us%20had%20stomach%20aches%20afterwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Sido%20recalled%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fmiddle-east%2Farticle-825066%5C%22%3EJerusalem%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20done%2C%20they%20told%20us%20that%20this%20was%20the%20meat%20of%20Yazidi%20babies.%20They%20showed%20us%20pictures%20of%20beheaded%20babies%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98these%20are%20the%20kids%20that%20you%20ate%20now.'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20woman%20suffered%20heart%20failure%20and%20died%20shortly%20after%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Sido%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20one%20mother%20even%20recognised%20her%20own%20child%20because%20of%20the%20baby's%20hands.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20forced%20us.%20But%20it's%20very%20hard%20to%20know%20that%20it%20happened.%20But%20it%20was%20not%20in%20our%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFawzia%20Sido%20was%20one%20of%20many%20Yazidi%20women%20enslaved%20by%20ISIS%20in%202014%20during%20the%20group's%20reign%20of%20terror.%20The%20Yazidis%2C%20a%20religious%20minority%20in%20northern%20Iraq%2C%20were%20subjected%20to%20unimaginable%20horrors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sido's%20revelation%20follows%20previous%20accusations%20that%20ISIS%20fed%20human%20meat%20to%20their%20captives.%20Yazidi%20parliamentarian%20Vian%20Dakhil%20first%20brought%20this%20practice%20to%20light%20in%202017%2C%20but%20Ms%20Sido's%20firsthand%20account%20is%20one%20of%20the%20clearest%20confirmations%20of%20this%20depravity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFawzia%20Sido's%20ordeal%20did%20not%20end%20with%20the%20forced%20consumption%20of%20human%20flesh.%20She%20was%20held%20captive%20for%20nine%20months%20in%20an%20underground%20prison%20alongside%20200%20other%20Yazidi%20women%20and%20children.%20Some%20of%20the%20children%20died%20due%20to%20contaminated%20water.%20Ms%20Sido%20was%20also%20sold%20to%20multiple%20jihadi%20fighters%2C%20including%20Abu%20Amar%20al-Makdisi%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20captivity%2C%20she%20was%20rescued%20by%20the%20IDF%20in%20a%20joint%20operation%20with%20the%20US%20Embassy%20and%20returned%20to%20her%20family%20in%20Iraq.%20However%2C%20her%20children%20remain%20in%20Gaza%20with%20her%20captor's%20family%2C%20where%20they%20are%20being%20raised%20as%20Arab%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUntil%20I%20got%20back%20to%20Iraq%2C%20I%20was%20all%20the%20time%20a%20%E2%80%98sabaya%2C'%20also%20in%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20using%20the%20Arabic%20term%20for%20a%20young%20woman%20held%20captive%20and%20exploited%20sexually.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729401060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F67oisrd8_fawzia-amin-sido_625x300_20_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyazidi-woman-freed-by-idf-from-gaza-reveals-isis-forced-them-to-eat-babies-6829920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fawzia%20Sido%20recounted%20how%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%20nine%2C%20she%20was%20captured%20along%20with%20her%20brothers%20and%20starved%20for%20three%20days.%20She%20was%20rescued%20by%20Israel%20from%20Gaza%20earlier%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyazidi-woman-freed-by-idf-from-gaza-reveals-isis-forced-them-to-eat-babies-6829920%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%20Vidya%20Ka%20Woh%20Wala%20Video%20crosses%2030%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729401019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114390394%2Cimgsize-18978.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Frajkummar-raos-vicky-vidya-ka-woh-wala-video-crosses-rs-30-crore-mark%2Farticleshow%2F1143904