%20to%20the%20history%20of%20the%2092-year-old%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%2C%20which%20is%20back%20at%20the%20helm%20in%20Srinagar%20with%20a%20clear%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20acts%20of%20the%20new%20popular%20government%20was%20to%20pass%20a%20resolution%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood.%20It%20received%20post-haste%20approval%20from%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Joshi.%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20is%20likely%20to%20travel%20to%20New%20Delhi%20now%20to%20seek%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister's%20endorsement%E2%80%94marking%20a%20fast%20transition%20of%20normalcy%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201944%2C%20the%20party%20adopted%20a%20Left-oriented%20manifesto%20for%20economic%20emancipation%20that%20encompassed%20visions%20for%20education%2C%20women's%20rights%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20health%2C%20aiming%20for%20equitable%20development%20across%20all%20areas%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%20This%20manifesto%20was%20handed%20over%20as%20a%20memorandum%20of%20protest%20during%20the%20era%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Princely%20Dogra%20State%2C%20ruled%20by%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh.%20The%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%20manifesto'%20was%20drafted%20by%20B.P.L.%20Bedi%2C%20a%20Sikh%20who%20is%20now%20better%20recognised%20as%20the%20father%20of%20international%20actor%20Kabir%20Bedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20accession%20to%20India%20in%201947%2C%20the%20NC%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20Abdullah%2C%20whose%20party%20symbol%2C%20the%20plough%2C%20is%20emblazoned%20on%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20implemented%20agrarian%20reforms%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20in%201950.%20This%20abolished%20land-ownership%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Zamindari%20Abolition%20and%20Land%20Reforms%20Act%2C%20which%20was%20enacted%20two%20years%20later%2C%20in%201952%2C%20throughout%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20Tenancy%20laws%20were%20made%20more%20favourable%20to%20small%20farmers%2C%20resulting%20in%20reduced%20poverty%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sheikh%20was%20the%20second%20Muslim%20leader%20after%20Kamal%20Atat%C3%BCrk%20of%20Turkey%20to%20abolish%20Purdah%20for%20women%E2%80%94a%20move%20that%20has%20been%20undermined%20by%20Pakistan-inspired%20extremists%20since%201989.%20The%20vision%20of%20Naya%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20obscured%20by%20terrorism%20since%201989%3B%20now%20there%20is%20hope%20for%20its%20revival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaya%20Kashmir%202.0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah's%20policies%20since%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20attempts%20at%20creating%20a%20Naya%20Kashmir%202.0%2C%20which%20would%20involve%20integrating%20the%20geographical%20entity%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20into%20the%20national%20mainstream%20and%20providing%20equal%20rights%20to%20all%2C%20including%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%20The%20abolition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98temporary%20and%20transient'%20Articles%20370%20and%2035A%20has%20granted%20universal%20voting%20rights%20and%20ownership%20entitlements%20to%20all%20citizens%20of%20India%E2%80%94rights%20that%20were%20previously%20confined%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98state%20subjects%20of%20J%26amp%3BK'%20before%205%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20the%201944%20Naya%20Kashmir%20manifesto%2C%20an%20omnibus%20economic%20and%20social%20reform%20package%20has%20been%20implemented%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20under%20the%20President's%20Rule%2C%20negating%20anti-India%20sentiment%2C%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20high%20voter%20turnout%20during%20recent%20elections.%20Campaigning%20continued%20till%20midnight%2C%20contrasting%20with%20the%20political%20campaigns%20from%201989%20to%202019%2C%20which%20were%20limited%20to%20daylight%20hours%20due%20to%20the%20looming%20fear%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaya%20Kashmir%202.0%20received%20a%20landmark%20breakthrough%20as%20Omar%20Abdullah%20took%20his%20oath.%20In%202009%2C%20when%20he%20was%20last%20sworn%20in%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20he%20affirmed%20his%20true%20faith%20and%20allegiance%20to%20%E2%80%98the%20Constitution%20of%20the%20state%20as%20by%20law%20established'.%20In%202016%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20swore%20allegiance%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Riyasati%20Aay%C4%81m'%20(state%20statute).%20On%20October%2016%2C%20when%20he%20took%20office%E2%80%94marking%20the%20sixth%20time%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Abdullah%20family%20has%20been%20sworn%20in%20as%20CM%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%E2%80%94he%20pledged%20allegiance%20to%20%E2%80%98the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20as%20by%20law%20established'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mature%20Start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20has%20initiated%20decisive%20steps%20to%20avoid%20confrontation%20with%20the%20Union%20Government%20and%20its%20representative%2C%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha.%20His%20INDIA%20bloc%20ally%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20suggested%20during%20a%20thank-you%20rally%20in%20Jammu's%20Doda%20that%20Omar%20could%20consult%20him%20on%20%E2%80%98how%20to%20run%20a%20half%20government'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20ignored%20Kejriwal's%20suggestion%2C%20stating%20to%20the%20media%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20does%20getting%20into%20a%20fight%20with%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20from%20Day%20One%20help%20me%20address%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20voters%3F%E2%80%9D%20NC's%20Srinagar%20MP%2C%20Ruhullah%20Mehdi%2C%20reminded%20the%20AAP%20supremo%20that%20the%20NC%20requires%20no%20prodding%20from%20his%20party%2C%20which%20had%20supported%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20referred%20to%20Modi%20as%20%E2%80%98an%20honourable%20gentleman'%20who%20had%20promised%20in%20Parliament%20that%20statehood%20would%20be%20restored%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time%E2%80%94thus%20extending%20an%20olive%20branch%20to%20the%20Centre.%20He%20has%20categorically%20stated%20that%20the%20NC%20is%20%E2%80%98setting%20aside'%20its%20demand%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98future%20date%2C%20when%20a%20new%20government%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre'%E2%80%94signalling%20that%20seeking%20cooperation%2C%20rather%20than%20engaging%20in%20confrontation%2C%20will%20be%20his%20approach.%20This%20is%20a%20lesson%20that%20perhaps%20the%20AAP%20could%20learn%20from%20the%20NC%2C%20and%20possibly%20also%20one%20for%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20to%20reflect%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar's%20mature%20approach%20paid%20off%20when%20Lt%20Governor%20Sinha%20signed%20on%20the%20dotted%20line%20to%20approve%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood.%20His%20decision%20to%20de-hyphenate%20statehood%20from%20Article%20370%20may%20prove%20decisive%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Debate%20On%20Article%20370%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20abolition%20of%20Article%20370%20has%20been%20a%20core%20agenda%20for%20the%20BJP%20since%20its%20inception%20as%20the%20Bharatiya%20Jan%20Sangh%20on%20October%2021%2C%201951.%20Its%20clarion%20call%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eek%20desh%20mein%20do%20vidhan%2C%20do%20nishan%20nahin%20chalega%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20targeted%20both%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20separate%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20flag.%20It%20took%2068%20years%20to%20implement%20this%20agenda.%20The%20NC's%20decision%20to%20bide%20its%20time%20on%20its%20demand%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Articles%20370%20and%2035A%20is%20aimed%20at%20a%20long-term%20perspective%E2%80%94it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20affect%20the%20governance%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20today.%20This%20maturity%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20NC%20should%20be%20reciprocated%20by%20the%20BJP%3B%20the%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20party%20must%20not%20create%20roadblocks%20for%20Modi-Shah's%20Naya%20Kashmir%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20of%202024%20have%20not%20only%20marked%20a%20triumph%20for%20the%20NC%20but%20also%20an%20assertion%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20polled%2025.64%25%2C%20achieving%20its%20highest-ever%20tally%20of%2029%20seats%20(all%20from%20Jammu)%2C%20while%20the%20NC%2C%20with%2023.43%25%2C%20won%2075%25%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20(35)%20and%20seven%20seats%20from%20Jammu.%20Congress%2C%20with%2011.97%25%2C%20has%20recorded%20its%20worst-ever%20tally%20of%20six%20seats.%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20three%20seats%2C%20while%20Sajjad%20Lone's%20People's%20Conference%20and%20Engineer%20Rashid's%20Awami%20Ittehad%20Party%20have%20been%20wiped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%208%2C%20while%20addressing%20triumphant%20BJP%20workers%20at%20the%20party's%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyay%20Marg%20headquarters%2C%20Modi%20extended%20his%20felicitations%20to%20the%20NC.%20On%20October%2016%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20congratulated%20Omar%20Abdullah%20on%20his%20swearing-in%20and%20posted%20on%20%E2%80%98X'%3A%20%E2%80%98Wishing%20him%20the%20very%20best%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20serve%20the%20people.%20The%20Centre%20will%20work%20closely%20with%20him%20and%20his%20team%20for%20J%26amp%3BK's%20progress.'%20Omar%20responded%20on%20X%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98My%20colleagues%20and%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20together%20with%20you%20to%20provide%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20an%20effective%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20honest%20administration.'%20Naya%20Kashmir%202.0%20has%20been%20launched%20with%20fervour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Well-Balanced%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20the%20NC%20solidified%20its%20position%20by%20approaching%20Congress%20rebels%20who%20had%20won%2C%20thus%20garnering%20the%20support%20of%20five%20Independent%20MLAs%20and%20increasing%20its%20strength%20to%2047%20in%20a%20House%20of%2090.%20It%20also%20enjoys%20the%20outside%20support%20of%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20and%20one%20each%20from%20AAP%20and%20CPM%2C%20effectively%20holding%2055%20out%20of%2090%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20has%20stated%20that%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Jammu%20region%20will%20be%20respected%3B%20thus%2C%20despite%20the%20overwhelming%20number%20of%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Kashmir%20division%2C%20three%20of%20the%20six%20ministers%20sworn%20in%20are%20from%20the%20Jammu%20region.%20Kejriwal's%20plea%20for%20his%20sole%20MLA%20to%20be%20included%20was%20ignored.%20Although%20Congress%20is%20attempting%20to%20take%20the%20moral%20high%20ground%20by%20stating%20it%20will%20join%20the%20government%20only%20after%20statehood%20is%20restored%2C%20Omar's%20deliberate%20avoidance%20of%20sharing%20a%20platform%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20suggests%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20Congress's%20abrasive%20politics%20in%20order%20to%20build%20bridges%20with%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20no%20point%20did%20the%20NC%20share%20Congress's%20doubts%20regarding%20the%20fairness%20of%20the%20poll%20process.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20polls%20are%20a%20slap%20in%20the%20face%20for%20those%20doubting%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHopefully%2C%20the%20worst%20is%20now%20behind%20J%26amp%3BK.%20No%20effort%20should%20be%20spared%20in%20achieving%20Naya%20Kashmir%202.0%E2%80%94with%20the%20present%20vision%20and%20an%2080-year-old%20legacy%20woven%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729397640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.c