%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-3-Rehab-1-1728640758-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-3-Rehab-1-1728640758-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-3-Rehab-1-1728640758-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESemchan%20Welfare%20Society%20also%20works%20towards%20rehabilitating%20injured%20stray%20dogs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20administer%20prescribed%20tablets%2C%20change%20wound%20dressings%2C%20apply%20topical%20medicines%2C%20and%20give%20physical%20therapy%20in%20some%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20making%20sure%20a%20dog%20exercises%2C%20or%20giving%20support%20to%20a%20dog%20learning%20to%20walk%20with%20a%20new%20injury%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20building%20more%20shade%20structures%20and%20expanding%20the%20open%20play%20area.%20We%20need%20to%20build%20one%20more%20room%20soon%20that%20will%20become%20an%20isolation%20ward%20for%20recovering%20dogs%20and%20those%20suffering%20from%20diseases%20like%20Parvo%2C%20and%20a%20food%20storage%20room.%20We%20want%20to%20improve%20our%20landscaping%20throughout%20the%20space%2C%20which%20will%20include%20plants%2C%20irrigation%2C%20stone%20retaining%20walls%2C%20steps%2C%20and%20pathways.%20We%20also%20want%20to%20dig%20a%20borewell%20by%20the%20next%20tourist%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(If%20you%20want%20to%20volunteer%2C%20please%20contact%20Arun%20Kumar%20at%209622143432.%20You%20can%20also%20follow%20Semchan%20Welfare%20Society%20on%20Instagram%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsemchanwelfaresociety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22