%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20believes%20that%20every%20individual%20has%20their%20own%20strengths%2C%20and%20opportunities%20should%20be%20offered%20to%20them%20based%20on%20those%20strengths.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20this.%20Every%20individual%20has%20their%20own%20strengths.%20Opportunities%20should%20be%20offered%20to%20them%20based%20on%20that%20strength.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20be%20educated%2C%20we%20should%20encourage%20them%20to%20finish%20their%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Sensitise%20the%20local%20officials%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20sensitise%20police%20and%20other%20support%20systems.%20If%20cases%20of%20domestic%20violence%20or%20sexual%20violence%20are%20informed%20to%20them%2C%20they%20need%20to%20respond%20with%20utmost%20care%20and%20urgency.%20It%20is%20not%20like%20dealing%20with%20regular%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20opines%20Prasanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Support%20your%20neighbours%20experiencing%20abuse%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20government%20officials%2C%20Prasanna%20believes%20it%20is%20our%20shared%20responsibility%20to%20not%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20such%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COften%2C%20when%20these%20incidents%20happen%2C%20neighbours%20feel%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20their%20place%20to%20intervene.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20duty%20to%20offer%20support.%20We%20need%20to%20organise%20programmes%20and%20discussions%20that%20actively%20involve%20community%20members%20in%20decision-making%20and%20foster%20a%20collective%20effort%20to%20tackle%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20assistance%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Prasanna%20through%20the%20Dhwani%20National%20Domestic%20Violence%20Hotline%20at%201800-102-7282%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%